title: Windows 7 Ultimate x64 original.iso
description:
Windows 7 Ultimate x64 official untouched ISO image



Minimum hardware requirements for Windows 7

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Processor 	  -    1 GHz x86-64 processor

Memory (RAM) 	  -    2 GB

Graphics card 	  -    DirectX 9 graphics processor with WDDM driver model 1.0
                          (Not absolutely necessary; only required for Aero)

Free hard drive   -    20 GB

Optical drive 	  -    DVD-ROM drive[93] (Only to install from DVD-ROM media)
